oso bucco

tie each round around tight
salt, and flour (shake off flour)

** all finly chopped
onions
carrots
celery
orange juice
lemon/orange rinds
crushed tomatos
rosemary
bay leave
juniper berries
clove
vermout

bown meats in olive oil and veg oil. carmelize each sides. remove.

brown the chopped veggies, add re-add meats. add remaining things and salt to taste. bring to boil, cover, put on simmer.

serve over rissoto milanese
